description:
&lt;p&gt;Connect Healthcare Rotherham CIC are the Rotherham GP Federation. We support all 30 Rotherham GP Practices. Rotherham have pioneered new workforce models and have already seen the benefit of Practice based pharmacists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join the NHS England Practice Pharmacist Scheme. This role will be based across a number of practices in Rotherham. The scheme also includes mentorship from a Senior Practice based Pharmacist and an 18 month tailored NHS England education program. Included in the training program is Independant Prescribing training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will support and manage a small team of pharmacists working across Rotherham.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The clinical pharmacists provide expertise in medication reviews, support patients to manage long-term conditions through medicines optimisation and improve patient care by increasing communication between general practice, community and hospital pharmacy.&lt;/p&gt;
